{"absolute_url":"https://www.thoughtworks.com/careers/jobs/5531780?gh_jid=5531780","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null}],"education":"education_required","internal_job_id":2732243,"location":{"name":"Beijing"},"metadata":[{"id":25172,"name":"Country","value":"China","value_type":"single_select"},{"id":25173,"name":"Job Role","value":"Business Analyst","value_type":"single_select"},{"id":25175,"name":"Link to Video","value":"https://thoughtworks.wistia.com/medias/rm8kwhlh0m","value_type":"url"},{"id":17181,"name":"Employment Type","value":"Regular","value_type":"single_select"},{"id":61790,"name":"Job Grade","value":"Lead Consultant","value_type":"single_select"},{"id":15975856,"name":"Function","value":["Engineering & Technology"],"value_type":"multi_select"},{"id":15976164,"name":"Remote Eligible","value":false,"value_type":"yes_no"}],"id":5531780,"updated_at":"2023-11-27T03:47:12-05:00","requisition_id":"5054","title":"Lead Business Analyst 资深业务分析师(Date&AI)(On-site)","pay_input_ranges":[],"content":"\n \n\n岗位职责\n\n\n研究并理解客户的战略、商业模式，挖掘并揭示客户的痛点和诉求\n帮助客户识别商业机会并建议实施方案\n引导需求探寻和创新思考工作坊，产出客户认可的解决方案\n创建并清楚展示方案蓝图，确保客户和交付团队理解并达成共识\n定义关键目标、成功要素，识别风险、挑战、依赖和约束\n有效引导和促进Product Owner、客户出资人、行业专家、技术团队、最终用户间的沟通和协作，保证产品从概念、到原型、到上线及运营的端到端交付\n成为客户值得信赖和依靠的工作伙伴\n用并提升客户的设计思维、敏捷和精益软件交付能力\n持续保有对新市场、新产品、新技术的学习热情，有积累和沉淀\n支持并参与售前、社区活动\n\n\n我们的要求\n\n技术技能\n\n\n具有广阔的视野，具备对复杂企业所处行业、运营模式、业务流程的理解和洞察力\n曾经经历过若干软件交付项目\n经历过识别需求、拆分需求、细化需求并交付需求的过程\n在业务、功能、技术问题上都有较强的理解力，能有效阐述和表达\n丰富的数据或者人工智能领域的项目经验\n\n\n专业技能\n\n\n喜欢全球化的工作环境，较多的英语表达和交流\n具有较强的团队协作、会议引导能力\n具有识别利益相关者，并有效管理和处理其间冲突的经历\n对前述挑战有浓厚的兴趣，喜欢接受挑战，学习能力强\n\n\n\n其它你可以了解的\n\n学习与发展\n\n在 Thoughtworks 没有一刀切的职业道路您的职业发展完全取决于您个人。同时我们也会平衡自主权与我们的文化。您的职业生涯也会有互动工具、众多发展计划和愿意帮助您成长的同事的支持。我们认为互相帮助是我们最好的价值，这是我们的员工职业生涯中赋予他们权力。\n\n\n关于Thoughtworks\n\nThoughtworks 是一家集战略、设计和工程推动数字创新为一体的全球技术咨询公司。 30 多年来，我们团队提供的卓有成效的解决方案赢得了客户的持续信任。在这里有计算机科学专业的毕业生，也有经验丰富的技术人员，有自学成才的开发人员、也有中途加入的人员，大家共同学习、面临挑战。大家的职业生涯因为加入我们而得到了更好发展，我们也因此在世界各地获得了无数奖项。 加入 Thoughtworks ，持续成长。让我们一起用好奇心、创新、热情和奉献精神超越平凡。\n\n#LI-Onsite","departments":[{"id":5744,"name":"Professional Services","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":11304,"name":"Beijing","location":"Beijing, China","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":11312,"name":"Shanghai","location":"Shanghai, China","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}],"compliance":null,"demographic_questions":null,"questions":[{"description":null,"label":"First Name","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"first_name","type":"input_text","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Last Name","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"last_name","type":"input_text","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Email","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"email","type":"input_text","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Phone","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"phone","type":"input_text","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Resume/CV","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"resume","type":"input_file","values":[]},{"name":"resume_text","type":"textarea","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Cover Letter","required":false,"fields":[{"name":"cover_letter","type":"input_file","values":[]},{"name":"cover_letter_text","type":"textarea","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Country","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"question_44196805","type":"input_text","values":[]}]},{"description":null,"label":"Would you require visa sponsorship to work in the country in which this position is based?","required":true,"fields":[{"name":"question_44196806","type":"multi_value_single_select","values":[{"label":"Yes","value":1},{"label":"No","value":0}]}]},{"description":null,"label":"LinkedIn Profile","required":false,"fields":[{"name":"question_44196807","type":"input_text","values":[]}]},{"description":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">进一步了解我们如何使用您的信息，</span><a href=\"https://www.thoughtworks.com/cn/online-application-consent\" target